    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl325_LabelType\">You are used to walking on wet and slippery surfaces.</span></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl325_LabelType\">Undine</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Benefits</strong></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl325_LabelType\">You are always considered to have firm footing when fighting underwater, and you gain a +2 trait bonus on Acrobatics checks and Climb checks on wet surfaces or in wet terrain, including bogs, standing or running water, or a storm-tossed ship.</span></p>",
